title: 56: The 100-Calorie Episode: Ways to Save, Burn & More!

description: It’s the CALORIE-SAVING EPISODE you’ve been waiting for!!! This week, Lisa shares tips and tricks for unexpected ways to save and burn 100 calories, plus creative 100-calorie couples that will change the way you snack forever! So lace up those shoes and grab your headphones, because you could BURN 100 calories just from walking while listening to this episode of CHEW THE RIGHT THING! www.hungry-girl.com/foodcast
